Task 1. Create a Linux VM instance

  Goto Compute Engine -> VM Instannces -> Create Instance.

     Name : apache
     Zone : us-central1-a
     Series : N1
     Boot Disk : Linux 9 (stretch)

     Tick : Allow HTTP Traffic
            Allow HTTPS Traffic

  -> Click Create.
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
Task 2. Enable public access to VM instance
    sudo su -
    apt-get update
    apt-get install apache2 -y
    service --status-all
    
   -> Click on External IP of 'apache' instance.
